---
import {ViewTransitions} from 'astro:transitions'
import { Picture } from 'astro:assets'

import Leader from '../layouts/Leader.astro'

import kidsLine from '../assets/images/photos/kids_line.jpg'
import tomoe from '../assets/images/photos/splash_kata.jpg'
import beach from '../assets/images/photos/shane_smash_beach.jpg'
import kugatsuLogo from '../assets/images/kugatsu.png'
import jitakyoeiLogo from '../assets/images/jitakyoei.png'
---
<Leader title="Home">
  <section>
    <Picture src={kidsLine} formats={['avif', 'webp', 'png']} width="1024" alt="Kids Line" />
    <p>
      Immerse yourself in the exciting fusion of Kugatsu Erina and Jita Kyoei Martial Arts Judo clubs as
      we proudly unveil our newly united club!
    </p>
    <p>
      Our approach blends the best of both worlds, offering a versatile martial arts experience that
      emphasizes techniques, discipline, and a sense of community.
    </p>
    <p>
      With expert guidance from our skilled instructors, our curriculum encompasses groundwork, throws,
      and self-defense â€“ creating a harmonious balance between strength and artistry.
    </p>
    <Picture src={tomoe} formats={['avif', 'webp', 'png']} width="1024" alt="Tomoe Nage Throw" />
    <p>
      Whether you're a seasoned martial artist or a newcomer eager to explore, our club provides a
      welcoming space for personal growth and camaraderie. Join us in embracing this new chapter, where the
      synergy of Jita Kyoei and Kugatsu Erina results in a unique martial arts journey tailored to the
      diverse interests and aspirations of our members.
    </p>
    <Picture src={beach} formats={['avif', 'webp', 'png']} width="1024" alt="Beach Throw" />
  </section>
  <section>
    <div class="logos">
      <Picture src={kugatsuLogo} formats={['avif', 'webp', 'png']} width="256" alt="Kugatsu Logo" />
      <Picture src={jitakyoeiLogo} formats={['avif', 'webp', 'png']} width="256" alt="Jita Kyoei Logo" />
    </div>
  </section>
</Leader>

<style>
section {
  @apply flex flex-col gap-4 w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-6;

  .logos {
    @apply mx-auto grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:gap-8 lg:gap-12;
  }

  img {
    @apply w-full mx-auto max-w-xl;
  }

  h1 {
    @apply text-center sm:text-left font-bold text-2xl;
  }

  h4 {
    @apply font-bold;
  }

  > div {
    @apply flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-2 lg:gap-4;

    div {
      @apply flex flex-col gap-2;
    }
  }
}
</style>
